jalse.actions

Class MultiActionBuilder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • jalse.actions.MultiActionBuilder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of actor to be supplied (can be ? for no actor).

    public final class MultiActionBuilder<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    An Action builder for creating Actions that chain, schedule or await other actions. This is useful for when some operations cannot be done out of sequence but the ActionEngine is a concurrent one.

    Actions can be easily chained with buildChain(Action...).
    Author:
    Elliot Ford
    See Also:
    ForkJoinActionEngine, ThreadPoolActionEngine
